Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akawaambia, \"Msiwadhulumu watu, wala msiwashtaki kwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uongo, ridhikeni na mshahara wenu.\" Watu wakashikwa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na udadisi, wote wakajiuliza mioyoni mwao kama huyu Yohane </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni Masiya mwenyewe au sivyo. Yohane akawapa wote jibu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lake akisema, \"Mimi nawabatiza kwa maji tu, lakini anakuja mmoja </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aliye na nguvu kuliko mimi. Hata sistahili kufungua ukanda wa viatu </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>vyake. Yeye atawabatiza kwa Roho Mtakatifu na kwa moto. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Anashika pepeo mkononi mwake ausafishe uwanda wake wa kupuria </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nafaka, kusudi akusanye ngano ghalani, bali makapi ayateketeze </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa moto usiozimika.\" 
