Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MŨRATHI BARUK: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jerusalem, ruta nguo yaku ya runo na thĩĩna, ĩkĩra ũthaka wa ũkumio </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Ngai hĩndĩ ciothe,wĩhumbe gĩthii gĩa kwĩhoka Ngai, ĩkĩra kĩraũni </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩa ũkumio wa mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ mũtwe-inĩ waku: tondũ Ngai nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ekwonania ũnene waku kũrĩ ndũrĩrĩ  ciothe iria irĩ ruungu rũa matu,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa Ngai egũkũhe hĩndĩ ciothe nĩ “Thayũ na njĩra ya wĩhokeku, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gĩtĩo na njĩra ya ũhoreri” Ũkĩra Jerusalem, rũgama na ũrũrie maitho </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maku mwena wa irathĩro: cũthĩrĩria ciana ciaku icokanĩrĩire ciumĩte </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwena wa irathĩro na ithũĩro na njĩra ya watho wa “ũrĩa Mũthure” </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikenete atĩ Ngai nĩ aciririkana. Ona gũtuĩka ciagũtigire na magũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itongoretio nĩ thũ, rĩu Ngai nĩ egũcicokia kũrĩ we ihana ta ihĩĩ cia </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anene igĩcokio kwao na ũkumio.  Tondũ Ngai nĩ athanĩte irĩma </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciothe ndaihu ciaraganio, o na tũrĩma twothe tũrĩa tũtũraga hĩndĩ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciothe, na mĩkuri yothe ĩiyũrio nĩ guo thĩ yothe ĩiganane nĩguo Israeli </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ahote gũthiĩ wega arĩ ruungu rũa ũkumio wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mĩtitũ oro hamwe na mũtĩ oro wothe mũnungi wega nĩ ũkaheane  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩruru nĩ ũndũ wa Israeli wa watho wa Ngai; 
tondũ Ngai nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatongoria Israeli na ũkeni na ũtheri wa ũkumio wake </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamwe na tha ciake na wĩhokeku.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>
THABURI YA GŨCOKERWO
Thaburi 126:1-2ab;2cd-3;4-5;6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rĩrĩa Mwathani aagarũrire a Sion arĩa atahe akĩmainũkia-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twahaanire ta andũ mekũrota. Tũnua twitũ  hĩndĩ ĩo </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũkĩiyũra mĩtheko, nĩmĩ ciitũ igakĩiyũra mũkũngũiyo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ gũgĩkĩĩranwo atĩrĩ: Mwathani nĩ ekĩire andũ aya maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>manene! Ĩĩ-ni, nĩ maũndũ manene Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aatwĩkĩire, na ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wamo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ Mwathani, kĩrĩkie kũgarũra atahwo aitũ mainũke, ta ũrĩa njũĩ cia Gũthini </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icokaga kũiyũra. Arĩa marahanda na </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maithori makagetha o magĩkũngũyagia </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndũ o na angĩthiĩ akĩrĩraga akuuĩte mbegũ agĩcihandaga, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũcoka agacoka agĩkũngũyagia, e na itĩa ciake cia ngano.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Mwathani, ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wa kĩhoti gĩaku.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Afilipi 1:4-6;8-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ndĩmũthaithanagĩrĩra, nĩ kũhoya ndĩmũhoyagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngenete, nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa tũgwatanĩire na inyuĩ kũhunjanĩria </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũhoro-ũrĩa-mwega, kuuma o mũthenya ũrĩa wa kwambĩrĩria o nginya rĩu. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ngakĩmenya ũndũ ũyũ na ma, atĩ we ũrĩa waambĩrĩirie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wĩra mwega thĩinĩ wanyu nĩ akaũrĩkia o nginya Mũthenya ũrĩa wa Yesu Kristũ.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ Ngai nĩwe mũira wakwa wa ũrĩa ndĩmwĩriragĩria inyuothe ndĩ na tha </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o iria ii na Yesu Kristũ. Na ũrĩa ‘hoyaga nĩ atĩrĩ, atĩ wendani wanyu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũingĩhage o kũingĩha makĩria, mũkĩongagĩrĩrũo ũmenyi o na ũkuũku </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wothe, nĩ getha mũhotage gũkũũrana maũndũ mũgĩthuraga marĩa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maagĩrĩire kũrĩ marĩa mangĩ, na mũtũũre mũtarĩ na ũhinga, na mũtarĩ</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũndũ ũngĩmũhĩtithia, o nginya rĩrĩa Mũthenya wa Kristũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgakinya; na ningĩ atĩ mũtũũre mũiyũrĩtwo nĩ maciaro ma </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũthingu, marĩa monekaga na ũndũ wa Yesu Kristũ, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha Ngai agoocagwo na akumagio.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Luka 3:4,6
	</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya. Thondekai kĩng’aratua kĩa Mwathani, rũngariai njĩra ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na andũ othe nĩ makona kũhonokania kũrĩa kwa Ngai. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 3:1-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, rĩrĩa Tiberio Cesare aathamakĩte mĩaka ikũmi na ĩtano, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o hĩndĩ ĩo, nĩ Pontio Pilato warĩ barũthi wa gwathaga Judea,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Herode aarĩ mũthamaki wa mabũrũri ma Iturea na Tarakonitide, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Lisania aarĩ mũthamaki wa Abilene. Hĩndĩ ĩo-rĩ, rĩrĩa Anna na Kaifa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maarĩ athĩnjĩri-Ngai arĩa anene, Ũhoro wa Ngai ũgĩkinya kwĩ John mũrũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Zakaria, e werũ-inĩ.  Nake agĩkinya ng’ongo  ciothe iria ciarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakuhĩ na Jordano, akĩhunjagia atĩ  andũ mabatithio,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o arĩa merirĩte, nĩguo moherũo mehia mao; o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ibuku-inĩ rĩa mohoro ma Isaia mũrathi, atĩrĩ:
He mũgambo </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra  werũ-inĩ, akoiga: Thondekai </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩng’aratua kĩa Mwathani, rũngariani njĩra ciake.  Ihuhi ciothe </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ igathikwo, ciambatĩre, nacio irĩma ciothe o na ithũngũri ciothe </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyihio ciaraganio; nakuo kũrĩa kuogomu kũrũngario, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kũrĩa gũtarĩ kwaraganu kwaraganio wega; o na andũ othe nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makona kũhonokania kũrĩa kwa Ngai.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA RIUKIRO MWAKA C"},{Guid:"Un1IKGr9UUGrbEEfXKiTjw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA RIUKIRO MWAKA C</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Sofonia 3;14-18 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA SOFONIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ, wee mwarĩ wa Sion, ina rũĩmbo, o nawe Israeli-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anĩrĩra mũno; o nawe mwarĩ wa Jerusalem canjamũka,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na ũkene na ngoro yaku yothe, Mwathani nĩ akuoheire </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agatiga gũkũhingĩria matuĩro ma cira waku, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio thũ ciaku nĩ acithinĩkanĩtie; mũthamaki </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Israeli arĩ thĩinĩ waku, nake nĩwe Mwathani;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee ndũgacoka kũonerũo kĩrĩi  o na rĩ.  Mũthenya ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jerusalem rĩkerũo atĩrĩ: Menya ũkanetigĩra; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o narĩo Sion rĩĩrũo atĩrĩ: Menya ũkanaregeria moko 
maku. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai waku arĩ thĩinĩ waku,
o we ũrĩa hoti </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya kũhonokania; nĩ arĩgũkenagĩra agũthererie ngoro, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na agũkĩrĩre nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa akwendete mũno; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agagũkũngũĩra na ndũrũhĩ cia nyĩmbo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Isaia 12:2-3;4bcd;5-6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ, Mwathani nĩwe ũhonokio wakwa, na nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndĩrĩĩhokaga na ndicoke gwĩtigĩra; Mwathani nĩwe hinya wakwa,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na nĩwe ndĩrĩinagĩra; nĩwe ũtuĩkĩte ihonokero rĩakwa.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ũcio mũgatahaga maaĩ ithima cia ũhonokanio mũkenete.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gathai Mwathani; hoyagai mũkĩgwetaga rĩĩtwa rĩake; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũmburĩrai andũ maũndũ marĩa ekaga, mũkĩmeraga </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ rĩĩtwa rĩake nĩ itũũgĩrie mũno.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Inĩrai Mwathani, nĩ ũndũ nĩ ekĩte maũndũ me ngumo nene, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũtũme ũhoro ũcio ũmenyũo thĩ yothe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee ũtũũraga Sion, anĩrĩra na mũgambo mũnene </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgũũthũke mũno, nĩ gũkorũo Ũrĩa Mũtheru wa Israeli, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ũcio ũrĩ thĩinĩ wanyu, nĩ mũnene mũno.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Inĩrai na gĩkeno Mũtheru wa Israeli</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Afilipi 4:4-7</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ikaragai mũkenete nĩ ũndũ wa Mwathani hĩndĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe: o na nguuga o rĩngĩ atĩ mũikarage mũkenete.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tũmagai gũkiranĩrĩria kwanyu kũmenyũo nĩ andũ othe.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani akiriĩ gũũka.Tigagai gwĩtanga nĩ ũndũ o na </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩkũ: no rĩrĩ, menyithagiai Ngai maũndũ marĩa mothe mwendaga,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkĩmũhoyaga na mũkĩmũthaithaga, hamwe na kũmũcokeria </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngatho. Naguo thayũ wa Ngai,
ũrĩa ũtangĩmenyeka ũrĩa ũtariĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũrĩikaragia ngoro cianyu o na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwĩciria kwanyu nakuo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI	</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya. Muoyo wa Mwathani arĩ Igũrũ rĩakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩni ũhoro ũrĩa mwega. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 3:10-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo andũ a kĩrĩndĩ makĩmũũria John atĩrĩ: Korũo nĩ ũguo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? Nake agĩcokia akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũrĩa wĩna nguo igĩrĩ, nĩ ahe ũrĩa ũtarĩ; nake ũrĩa wĩna irio-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ekage ũguo.  Ningĩ gũgĩũka etia mbia cia igoti  makabatithio, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao makĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Mũrutani, ithuĩ twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũtigetie andũ kĩndũ tiga o kĩrĩa mwathĩtwo mwĩtagie. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao athigari makĩmũũria atĩrĩ: Na ithuĩ-rĩ, twagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩkaga atĩa? </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũtikananyarire mũndũ, o na kana mũtunye mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩndũ nĩ kũmũigĩrĩra; na ningĩ mũiganagwo nĩ mũcara wanyu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩatanyaga, gĩgĩthanganagia, nao andũ othe </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mageciragia ngoro-inĩ ciao ũhoro wa John, kana hihi nĩwe Kristũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>John agĩcokia akĩmera othe atĩrĩ: Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩmũbatithagia </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na maĩ; no rĩrĩ, nĩ gũgoka ũngĩ wĩna hinya kũrĩ niĩ, nayo mĩkwa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya iratũ ciake, niĩ-rĩ, ndiigaine  wa kũmĩohora; ũcio nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkamũbatithagia  na Muoyo Mũtheru o na mwaki: gĩtarũrũ gĩake  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩ nakĩo guoko, nĩ getha  atherie wega kĩhuhĩro gĩake, nacio ngano </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>acokererie aciite ikũmbĩ rĩake; 
no acine mũũngũ na mwaki ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtangĩhoreka. Ũguo noguo aahunjagia Ũhoro ũrĩa Mwega, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩtaaraga andũ na maũndũ mangĩ maingĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,
