Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia; Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tucokerere, Ngai mwene mbutu cia ita, twaguthaitha</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikia maitho wi kuu iguru, wone, ukirore muthabibu uyu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Oguo muti uria gwoko gwaku kwa urio kwahandire,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ruo ruhonge ruria werereire ni bata waku mwene</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia; Ii camai muone ati Mwathani ni mwega</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mundu ucio wahandirwo guoko gwaku kwa urio-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
