Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA RĨA MAANDĨKĨIRUO KŨRĨ ANDŨ AHEBEREA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, Kristũ, agĩũka gũkũ thĩ, ekuuga atĩrĩ: Wee-rĩ, ti </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magongona na mahaki wendaga,
no nĩ mwĩrĩ ũthondekeire; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mahaki ma gũcinwo, na ma kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>timo ũkenagĩra.  Hĩndĩ  ĩo ngĩuga  atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ! Ndĩ gũũka, thĩinĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa ibuku o rĩo rĩa gĩkũnjo, 
uhoro wakwa nĩho wandĩkĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wendaga, wee Ngai. Nake oiga hau mbere </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ magongona ma mahaki, na mahaki ma gũcinwo, na marĩa ma </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũrutwo nĩ ũndũ wa mehia timo wendaga kana ũkamakenera-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>namo nĩmo marutagwo ta ũrĩa gwathanĩtwo watho-inĩ, agacoka </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akoiga : Atĩrĩ, ndĩ gũũka gwĩkaga o ũrĩa wee wendaga. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ kweheria ekweheria ũhoro ũcio wa mbere, nĩ getha arũmie ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa kerĩ. Nakuo kwenda kũu nĩkuo gũtũmaga tũtherio, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa Yesu Kristũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>warutirũo o ihinda rĩmwe rĩa kũigana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Luka 1:38</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya. One ndungata ya Mwathani, nĩ njĩkũo ta ũrĩa woiga. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 1:39-56</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Maria nĩ okĩrire agĩthiĩ mĩtũkĩ irĩma-inĩ  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>itũra-inĩ rĩa Juda.  Na nĩ atonyire mũciĩ wa Zakaria,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>na akĩgeithia Elisabeth.  Na nĩ gwatuĩkire atĩ Elisabeth aigwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>ngeithi  cia Maria, kaana gagĩtũhatũha ndainĩ; nake Elisabeth </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>akĩiyũrũo nĩ Mũoyo Mũtheru; na agĩkaya na mũgambo mũnene, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>akiuga: Wee mũrathime kũrĩ aka othe, na ũciari wa nda </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>yaku nĩ mũrathime.  Na ũhoro ũyũ umĩte kũ, atĩ nyina wa Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>wakwa ũke kũrĩ niĩ? Amu mũgambo wa ngeithi ciaku </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>watonya matũ-inĩ makwa, one, gakenge nĩ gatũhĩte na ũkeni </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>thĩinĩ wa nda yakwa. Na mũkeni nĩwe wĩtĩkĩtie, nĩ gũthima maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>marĩa werirũo nĩ Ngai nĩ makahingio. Na maria akiuga atirĩ, Ngoro yakwa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>nĩ ũkũgatha Ngai, na mũoyo wakwa ũgacanjamũka thĩinĩ wa Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>mũhonokia wakwa. Nĩ gũtuĩka nĩ acũthĩrĩirie wĩnyihia wa ndungata yake; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>amu oneni kwarũma rĩu njiarũa ciothe nĩ ikanjĩta mũkeni. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461> Nĩ ũndũ ũrĩa kĩhoti nĩ anjĩkire maũndũ  manene, na rĩĩtwa rĩake nĩ rĩtheru. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Na tha ciake  nĩ ikinyagĩra njiarũa, 
na njiarũa cia arĩa mamwĩtigagĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Nĩ ekĩte maũndũ marĩ hinya na guoko gwake; nĩ aharaganirie </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>arĩa anene  thĩ moime itĩ-inĩ ciao, na akĩnenehia arĩa anini.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Nĩ aiyũrĩtie arĩa  ahũtu na mawega, na itonga nĩ airekirie ũtheri.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Nĩ amũkĩrire Israeli ndungata  yake, akĩririkana tha ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>O ta ũrĩa erire maithe maitũ, Abraham na njiarwa ciake tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Na Maria nĩ aikaranirie nake ta </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>mĩeri ĩtatũ, na agĩcoka akĩinũka kwao.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3461>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Body:{Transition:0}},
